\id PHM - Biblica® Open Ndebele Contemporary Bible 
\h UFilimoni 
\toc1 Incwadi KaPhawuli KuFilimoni 
\toc2 UFilimoni 
\toc3 Flm 
\mt1 UFilimoni 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Mina Phawuli, isibotshwa sikaKhristu uJesu, loThimothi umzalwane wethu, 
\b  
\p KuFilimoni umngane wethu othandekayo loyisisebenzi kanye lathi,  
\v 2 ku-Afiya udadewethu, ku-Akhiphasi olibutho kanye lathi, lasebandleni elihlanganela ekhaya lakho ngithi: 
\b  
\p  
\v 3 Umusa kawube kuwe kanye lokuthula okuvela kuNkulunkulu uBaba leNkosini uJesu Khristu. 
\b  
\s1 Ukubonga Lokukhuleka 
\p  
\v 4 Ngihlezi ngimbonga kokuphela uNkulunkulu wami lapho ngikukhumbula emikhulekweni yami  
\v 5 ngoba ngiyezwa ngothando lwakho lokukholwa eNkosini uJesu kanye lothando lwakho kubo bonke abangcwele.  
\v 6 Ngikhulekela ukuba ukuhlanganyela kwakho kanye lathi ekukholweni kube lomfutho ngokujula ekuqedisiseni kwakho konke ukulunga esikwabelana ngenxa kaKhristu.  
\v 7 Uthando lwakho lungiphe ukuthokoza okukhulu lokududuzeka ngoba wena, mzalwane, uvuselele inhliziyo zabangcwele. 
\s1 Isikhalazo SikaPhawuli Ngo-Onesimasi 
\p  
\v 8 Ngakho-ke, lanxa kuKhristu ngingaba lesibindi ngikulaye ukuba wenze lokho okumele ukwenze  
\v 9 kodwa ngiyakuncenga ngenxa yothando. Ngakho-ke, mina Phawuli, umuntu omdala khathesi oyisibotshwa sikaKhristu uJesu futhi,  
\v 10 ngiyakuncenga ngenxa yendodana yami u-Onesimasi owaba yindodana yami ngibotshiwe.  
\v 11 Kuqala wayengelasizo kuwe kodwa khathesi uselusizo kuwe lakimi. 
\p  
\v 12 Ngimthuma kuwe yena othandwe yinhliziyo yami.  
\v 13 Kade ngingathanda ukuhlala laye ukuze athathe indawo yakho yokungisiza ngisabotshelwe ivangeli.  
\v 14 Kodwa angithandanga ukwenza lutho kungelamvumo yakho ukuze kuthi loba ngumusa owenzayo ube ngowokuzithandela hatshi ukubanjwa ngamandla.  
\v 15 Mhlawumbe isizatho sokwehlukaniswa lawe okwesikhatshana sasiyikuthi ube laye futhi kokuphela  
\v 16 engaseyiso sigqili kodwa esengcono kulesigqili njengomzalwane othandekayo. Uyathandeka kimi kodwa uthandeka kakhulu kuwe njengomunye wakho lanjengomzalwane eNkosini. 
\p  
\v 17 Ngakho-ke, nxa ungithatha njengohlanganyela lawe, mamukele ngendlela obuzangamukela ngayo.  
\v 18 Nxa kulokubi akwenze kuwe kumbe elesikwelede kuwe, kubalele kimi.  
\v 19 Mina Phawuli, ngiloba lokhu ngesandla sami. Ngizahlawula ngingabali ukuthi lawe ulomlandu kimi wena ngokwakho.  
\v 20 Ngiyafisa, mzalwane, ukuba ngithole usizo oluthile kuwe eNkosini; uvuselele inhliziyo yami kuKhristu.  
\v 21 Ngileqiniso ngokulalela kwakho, ngikulobela ngisazi ukuthi uzakwenza okudlula engikucelayo. 
\p  
\v 22 Okunye njalo yilokhu: Ngilungisela indlu yezihambi ngoba ngithemba ukuba ngizabuyiselwa kuwe ngenxa yemikhuleko yakho. 
\b  
\b  
\p  
\v 23 U-Ephafrasi oyisibotshwa kanye lami ngenxa kaKhristu uJesu, uyakubingelela. 
\p  
\v 24 UMakho, lo-Aristakhasi, loDemasi kanye loLukha abayizisebenzi kanye lami bayakubingelela. 
\b  
\p  
\v 25 Umusa weNkosi uJesu Khristu kawube lomoya wakho.